  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>礼なんていらないぜ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>No need for thanks.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>13</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>……何も言われてないだろう</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...They haven't even said anything.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>12</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>わたし達の服装が危険っていうか
そういう目でしか見られない
ティトレイが危ないんじゃないの？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It's not our clothes that are dangerous, it's that
you're looking us like that. Aren't you what's
dangerous here?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>27</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ああ、まったくだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yes, seriously.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>15</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>おれは変な目でなんか見てねぇよ。
二人とも、全然おれの好みじゃないしな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I'm not lookin' at you guys weird.
You guys ain't even my type.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>13</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>なにそれ！　そういう事言う！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What the heck?! You would just out and say that?!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>27</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>なんて無礼な男なんだ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What an impudent man!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>15</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>あ、あれ？
おれなんで怒られてんだ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>H-Huh?
Why're they yellin' at me?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>13</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ピーチパイはまだなのか……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Is my peach pie still not ready...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>12</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
